572
01:07:00,830 --> 01:07:01,920
Yi-gang!

573
01:07:03,260 --> 01:07:05,240
Aku baru mau meneleponmu.

574
01:07:05,870 --> 01:07:07,290
Hyun-jo.

575
01:07:08,850 --> 01:07:10,910
